the united states for failing to impose economic sanctions in 
retaliation for the embargo 
can the freedom of one group of people be sold for the freedom 
of another what then is the idea of freedom itself the 
lithuanian leader said in a statement released by his press office 
in vilnius the republics capital 
this is another munich landsbergis said referring to 
french and british appeasement of nazi germany that culminated in 
