the buffalo ny news on global warming 
if there is any hope to be found in results from the white house 
conference on global warming it is that several nations appear 
ready now to reduce pollution and prevent the devastating 
consequences that eventually could result from a heightening of the 
greenhouse effect 
unfortunately the bush administration which hosted the 
