rehabilitation work in areas burned by the major fires of 1987 in 
california oregon and washington and to high levels of 
reforestation in areas of 198688 timber harvests in the national 
forests 
of the total area reforested in the fiscal year that ended last 
sept 30 about 307000 acres were directly seeded or planted with 
trees the remaining 185000 acres were reforested through natural 
regeneration by seed falling from nearby trees onto areas prepared 
by the forest service or through sprouting 
