many members of the legislature the supreme soviet criticized 
the plan as inadequate to deal with the health agricultural 
economic and environmental aftermath of the ukraine accident 
legislator yuri scherback estimated 250 billion rubles 405 
billion are needed over the next 10 years 
official reports say 31 people were killed when one of four 
reactors at chernobyl caught fire and exploded april 26 1986 
unofficial reports say 250 died the blast spewed cesium strontium 
and plutonium across much of the ukraine byelorussia and russia 
