5 million more than planned to distribute the newspaper because 
twice as many readers as expected wanted their newspapers delivered 
advertisers consider that to be very good but its much more 
expensive than we planned for ingersoll said 
but home subscribers also were canceling their subscriptions at 
an extremely fast rate making it difficult for the sun to sign up 
enough new subscribers to keep circulation from falling 
