secede 
so the reshetov attempt to bend american history into a soviet 
parallel doesnt work but anarchy doesnt work either 
no one not soviets not lithuanians not americans wants to 
see the price half a million lives that was paid on american 
soil to establish the antisecessionist principle that lincoln laid 
down and reshetov would adopt as his own 
