sweetener users association which represents industrial consumers 
of sugar and other sweeteners 
quotas are used to restrict the amount of foreign sugar that can 
enter the united states thus protecting domestic producers from 
lowerpriced foreign sugar being dumped on the us market 
revised allocations announced by us trade representative carla 
